Uses of Package
popt4jlib.GA

  • Packages that use popt4jlib.GA 
    Package Description
    popt4jlib.GA
    Genetic Algorithms Parallel Implementation.
  • Classes in popt4jlib.GA used by popt4jlib.GA 
    Class and Description
    DGA
    The DGA class implements a thread-safe parallel Distributed Genetic Algorithm that follows the island-model of GA computation, with an elitist selection strategy that uses roulette-wheel selection of individuals based on their fitness (that is computed every generation).
    DGAIndividual
    auxiliary class not part of the public API.
    DGAIndividualPool
    The class is responsible for maintaining a sufficiently large array of DGAIndividual objects, and there will be a pool for each thread of execution.
    DGAThread
    auxiliary class not part of the public API.
    DGAThreadAux
    auxiliary class not part of the public API.
    IndComp
    auxiliary class not part of the public API.
    MutationOpIntf
    public interface for mutation operators.
    XoverOpIntf
    public interface for cross-over operators.
